=== System Optimization ===
#'''General'''
#*Optimized the performance of the reconnection feature;
#*Improved the display of remaining sale time for special furniture in Private Quarters under certain conditions;
#*Enhanced the display of locked character avatars in Private Quarters;
#*Added a tights on/off interaction feature in Private Quarters;
#*Introduced a Transport Jobs refresh function in Island Planner;
#*Optimized item detail displays in certain interfaces of Island Planner;
#*Fixed an issue where the Island Technology Café Manjuu Slot B was abnormally unlocked; already produced items will be automatically claimed after this maintenance;
#*Adjusted prices of fruit tree seeds in the Island Planner store;
#*Fixed an issue where Workerjuus in Island Planner were not displayed correctly under certain conditions;
#*Fixed an issue where daily and weekly plans in Island Planner failed to refresh properly under specific circumstances;
#*Fixed an issue where items on certain screens would not display correctly in some cases;
#*Fixed an issue where character interactions could not be executed properly under certain conditions;
#*Fixed an issue where some character data failed to display correctly in specific scenarios;
#*Fixed some UI, texts, and images.
